item.title: My newest 6 models
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

I’m not really a fan of your blades, they all look way too wide and not tall enough.
Usually devil wings are red or a color associated with dark (blue, not so much) but that’s just a color and nothing more.
The in game looks of the wings look amazing, but in the model view they look kind of matted and bland, they could use a ‘feathering’ effect.
As for Gandalf’s white staff, you can’t see a lot of it’s design in game, and therefore a lot of the detail you did add (see this image) isn’t needed.

Read full topic
